<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-526] Omni-Path: Change &quot;Intel&quot; to &quot;Cornelis Networks&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-526</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Please make the following Omni-Path updates to the Lustre Manual:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change&#160; &quot;OmniPath&quot; to &quot;Omni-Path&quot; in all instances&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change in 1.1.1 Lustre Features &#8230; Other Lustre software features are: ... &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;bullet 4&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; High-performance heterogeneous networking:The Lustre software &#8230; (OFED*), &lt;b&gt;Intel OmniPath&#174;&lt;/b&gt;, and other ...
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Change text in bold to &lt;b&gt;Cornelis Networks Omni-Path&lt;/b&gt;&#160; &#160;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&#160;Change in 16.1. Multi-Rail Overview ... , and &lt;b&gt;Intel&#174; Omni-Path&lt;/b&gt;. For Lustre clients ...
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Change text in bold to &lt;b&gt;Cornelis Networks Omni-Path&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
